<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Colorful HTML Snippet Playground</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f1021;
      --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      --text: #f7f7ff;
      --muted: #c7c7e5;
      --grad1: #6a11cb;
      --grad2: #2575fc;
      --grad3: #ff4d6d;
      --grad4: #f9c74f;
      --success: #2dd4bf;
      --danger: #ef4444;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 10%, #2a2b6f 0%, transparent 35%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 90% 20%, #92278f 0%, transparent 40%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #0b0c1d, #111232 50%, #161744 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .floating-bg {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .bubble {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(2px);
      opacity: 0.35;
      animation: float 14s infinite ease-in-out;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--grad2), var(--grad3));
    }

    .bubble:nth-child(1){ width:120px;height:120px;left:6%;top:14%; animation-delay:0s; }
    .bubble:nth-child(2){ width:80px;height:80px;left:75%;top:20%; animation-delay:2s; }
    .bubble:nth-child(3){ width:150px;height:150px;left:54%;top:67%; animation-delay:4s; }
    .bubble:nth-child(4){ width:95px;height:95px;left:19%;top:72%; animation-delay:1s; }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-25px) scale(1.08); }
    }

    .wrap { width: min(1200px, 92%); margin: 2rem auto 4rem; }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grad4), #fff, #8be9fd);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
      animation: shimmer 6s linear infinite;
      background-size: 300% 100%;
    }

    @keyframes shimmer { from { background-position: 0 0; } to { background-position: 300% 0; } }

    .subtitle { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .snippet {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1rem;
      transition: transform .35s ease, box-shadow .35s ease;
      animation: rise .7s ease both;
    }

    .snippet:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.3); }

    @keyframes rise { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

    h2 { margin: 0 0 .8rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }

    .btns { display: flex; gap: .6rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    button {
      border: none;
      color: white;
      padding: .6rem .9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .2s;
    }
    button:active { transform: scale(.95); }
    .btn-primary { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grad1), var(--grad2)); }
    .btn-danger { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff416c, #ff4b2b); }
    .btn-success { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #11998e, #38ef7d); }

    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: .3rem .6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin: .2rem;
      font-size: .85rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.2);
    }

    .loader {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
      border-top-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
      margin-top: .5rem;
    }
    @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    .progress {
      height: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-top: .6rem;
    }
    .progress > div {
      height: 100%;
      width: 70%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4, #fad0c4);
      animation: movebar 2.2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    @keyframes movebar { from { width: 30%; } to { width: 90%; } }

    input, select, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      margin: .35rem 0;
      padding: .6rem .7rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.2);
      color: white;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      font-size: .9rem;
    }
    th, td { padding: .5rem; text-align: left; }
    th { background: rgba(255,255,255,.2); }
    tr:nth-child(even){ background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); }

    .notification {
      padding: .7rem .9rem;
      border-left: 5px solid var(--success);
      background: rgba(45,212,191,.15);
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: .6rem;
    }

    code {
      display:block;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.26);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: .65rem;
      margin-top: .6rem;
      color: #d6f8ff;
      font-size: .8rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="floating-bg">
    <div class="bubble"></div><div class="bubble"></div><div class="bubble"></div><div class="bubble"></div>
  </div>

  <main class="wrap">
    <h1>Colorful Animated HTML Snippets</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Copy ideas from each block below: buttons, cards, forms, tables, loaders, alerts, and more.</p>

    <section class="grid">
      <article class="snippet">
        <h2>1) Fancy Buttons</h2>
        <div class="btns">
          <button class="btn-primary">Primary</button>
          <button class="btn-success">Success</button>
          <button class="btn-danger">Danger</button>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="snippet">
        <h2>2) Tags / Pills</h2>
        <span class="tag">#HTML</span>
        <span class="tag">#CSS</span>
        <span class="tag">#Animation</span>
        <span class="tag">#Colorful</span>
      </article>

      <article class="snippet">
        <h2>3) Loader</h2>
        <div class="loader"></div>
      </article>

      <article class="snippet">
        <h2>4) Animated Progress Bar</h2>
        <div class="progress"><div></div></div>
      </article>

      <article class="snippet">
        <h2>5) Mini Form</h2>
        <input placeholder="Your name" />
        <select><option>Pick a style</option><option>Neon</option><option>Soft</option></select>
        <textarea rows="3" placeholder="Message..."></textarea>
      </article>

      <article class="snippet">
        <h2>6) Data Table</h2>
        <table>
          <thead><tr><th>Theme</th><th>Level</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Galaxy</td><td>Easy</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Neon Pulse</td><td>Medium</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Aurora</td><td>Hard</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </article>

      <article class="snippet">
        <h2>7) Notification Alert</h2>
        <div class="notification">✅ Saved! Your colorful component is ready.</div>
      </article>

      <article class="snippet">
        <h2>8) Copy Example Block</h2>
        <code>&lt;button class="btn-primary"&gt;Click me&lt;/button&gt;</code>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
